```

## Notes

- Home volumes are shared across worktrees (keeps credentials)
- Container names are unique per worktree (no conflicts)
- Changes to `.devcontainer/devcontainer.json` are temporary
- Reset with: `git checkout .devcontainer/devcontainer.json`

## Integration

This command is automatically called by `/start-work` when creating a new worktree in a project with DevContainers.